    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Keep personal belongings or outdoor essentials secure and within reach, using ASR Outdoors locking carabiners, designed specifically for hiking, camping, fishing, and everyday outdoor adventures. The locking carabiners are made from lightweight, durable aluminum, and feature a screw-locking mechanism to ensure gear stays safely attached to bags, backpacks, jackets, belt loops and more.</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor 3 Inch Locking Aluminum Carabiner Clip EDC Camping Gear (3 Colors)</h2>\n  <p>Keep personal belongings or outdoor essentials secure and within reach, using ASR Outdoors locking carabiners, designed specifically for hiking, camping, fishing, and everyday outdoor adventures. The locking carabiners are made from lightweight, durable aluminum, and feature a screw-locking mechanism to ensure gear stays safely attached to bags, backpacks, jackets, belt loops and more.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>LOCKING CARABINERS:</strong> Carabiners keep personal belongings or other outdoor gear secure and safely clipped to bags, backpacks, belt loops, jackets or wherever you need to stash your stuff</li>\n    <li><strong>ALUMINUM CONSTRUCTION:</strong> Lightweight and rust resistant for long term use when camping, hiking, backpacking, to carry EDC gear and more</li>\n    <li><strong>MATTE FINISH:</strong> Choose from three colors, silver, black or olive green in modern and sleek matte finish</li>\n    <li><strong>KEYRING INCLUDED:</strong> Ready to deploy for keys, mini survival gadgets, lightweight tools and more</li>\n    <li><strong>SPECIFICATIONS:</strong> Length: 3.0 inches; Thickness: 8mm; Weight: 0.04lbs</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/72364/Jmq8khNsJgT7bk4MBKDjIYseTfhBoW-metaQVNST19sb2NraW5nX2NhcmFiaW5lcl9hbGxfY29sb3JzX21haW4ucG5n-.png\" alt=\"Keep personal belongings or outdoor essentials secure and within reach, using ASR Outdoors locking carabiners, designed specifically for hiking\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> ASR-3CARAB-PARENT</li>\n    <li><strong>Size:</strong> Mini</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>Each carabiner boasts an 8mm thick aluminum body, and weighs in at just 0.04lbs, meaning they’ll barely add any additional bulk or heaviness to gear, which can mean a lot when you’re backpacking, hiking or hauling gear from one spot to the next!</p>\n  <p>The trio of assorted colors (matte black, green or silver), allow you to easily color code items or match to existing outdoor gear. Each carabiner is compact enough to carry just about anywhere, yet tough enough to handle any daily routine. So, whether you&#039;re attaching keys to your belt loop, securing a water bottle to your backpack, or hanging a lantern in your tent, these ASR Outdoor locking carabiners deliver lightweight durability and dependable functionality. Their compact size and easy twist lock design make them reliable and convenient for both quick day or weekend trips and extended adventures alike.</p>\n  <p>PLEASE NOTE: These carabiners are NOT designed for climbing or heavy load-bearing applications</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
